<note id="fs-idm208938544" class="os-teacher">
<title>Full Text</title>
<para id="fs-idm227547312">Phil “Bo” Perabo, Letter Home <link url="https://www.nationalww2museum.org/war/articles/mail-call-bo-perabo-and-liberation-pacific">https://www.nationalww2museum.org/war/articles/mail-call-bo-perabo-and-liberation-pacific</link></para>
