<section id="fs-idm223201872">
<title>Comprehension Questions</title>
<exercise id="fs-idm241868032">
<problem id="fs-idm245930336">
<para id="fs-idm241156800">What injuries has Perabo experienced?</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idm228947504">
<problem id="fs-idm254859168">
<para id="fs-idm209122592">Who does Perabo blame for his circumstances of being shot down?</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idm224237776">
<problem id="fs-idm227613904">
<para id="fs-idm211113344">Despite the horrific treatment Perabo likely experienced at Ōfuna Camp, he is generally very positive throughout this letter. Why do you think he does this?</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idm240994656">
<problem id="fs-idm223271072">
<para id="fs-idm248767152">What do you think that Perabo means by this final line?</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
